Built in python 3 using the TVDB API

How to use:
Copy the nxtep.py file to /bin directory and run 
$ nxtep.py

nxtep : Returns release dates and synopsis of an episode from a tv show
Options : -n to specify the Name of the Series
	-s to specify the Season (must be a number)
	-e to specify the Episode number (type 'lt', without qoutes, to get the latest episode information) 
Get your API key by registering with Tvdb on http://thetvdb.com/?tab=login
and then obtain and add your JWT token here https://api.thetvdb.com/swagger (top right corner)
